videos.headline: Herrien extends Bulldogs' lead
videos.description: Brian Herrien runs eight yards for the second Georgia touchdown of the day vs. Kentucky.

videos.headline: Swift grabs 2nd TD of day
videos.description: De'Andre Swift dives into the end zone for his second touchdown of the day as the Bulldogs pad their lead over Kentucky.
